    "name": "Scriptish: Shrink Active Scripts Badge",
    "description": "Shrinks and moves the active scripts badge on the toolbar button so it doesn't push out the margins. Double digits will still push out, but not as much.",
    "additionalInfo": "I'm using my other script style 53817 to change the button icon. This style still works with the stock icon, but the green badge on green icon will look a bit strange.\r\n\r\n2012.02.24 - 54890 has a neat effect of turning the badge grey for the number 0; I added that to mine since I didn't want the other effects in that script. It's a cool script though, I'd probably use it but I think it would conflict with Greasefire.",
